{"tid":1204772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲係6·12生日","createTime":"2019-06-11T16:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T13:50:34.000Z","uid":24972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e673b3c089c1fdd2aa40deab49665c1aafc4d520","tid":1204772,"uid":24972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲係6月12日生日？<br />\n以前呢個時候會諗下去邊食飯，book咩餐廳，着咩衫去玩，去邊到玩⋯<br />\n今年嘅生日無豐富嘅大餐，浪漫嘅餐廳同好玩嘅行程，<br />\n但就比以前過得更有意義！<br />\n<br />\n短短十幾年，香港嘅變化大家都有目共睹，<br />\n無論係新聞自由，教育，醫療，經濟，環境，社會等各方面嘅情況都係每況愈下，<br />\n經過雨革，魚革同69遊行，感受到香港人嘅團結<br />\n香港人對家嘅愛。<br />\n<br />\n以後生日都會諗起，我地大家一齊努力過，爭取過，奮鬥過嘅日子！<br />\n最後 乞句生日快樂<br />\n誠邀大家一齊去野餐 參加我嘅生日party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑夜無論怎樣悠長，白晝總會到來</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2ALZ4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2ALZ4q.png&h=43e68d74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVudpv6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVudpv6.png&h=e384c34d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXqTpv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXqTpv7.png&h=0666f4b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a87037b9504f14172cb32a9cb76f50985a34b30f","tid":1204772,"uid":152313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"}]}